<h3 class=col-title>Toasting Etiquette</h3><span class=liner></span>
<div class=aside-content>
<ul id="glass_bullet">
 <li>The first toast given during a dinner is normally offered at the beginning of the meal.</li>
 <li>Traditionally, the first toast is offered by the host as a welcome to guests.</li>
 <li>Toasts offered by others start during the dessert course.</li>
</ul>
